title: BRIEF-Praxair Signs Long-Term Agreement To Supply Samsung Electro-Mechanics In Busan
text:
April 20, 2018 / 3:28 PM / in 8 minutes BRIEF-Praxair Signs Long-Term Agreement To Supply Samsung Electro-Mechanics In Busan Reuters Staff 
April 20 (Reuters) - Praxair Inc: 
* PRAXAIR SIGNS LONG-TERM AGREEMENT TO SUPPLY SAMSUNG ELECTRO-MECHANICS IN BUSAN, SOUTH KOREA 
* PRAXAIR INC - SIGNED A LONG-TERM AGREEMENT TO SUPPLY INDUSTRIAL GASES TO SAMSUNG ELECTRO-MECHANICS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
